// Applied via style:
<motion.div style={{ x: translation }} />
```

### 3f. `layout="size"` for accordion expand/collapse

From `/home/himmel/personal/prsui/registry/new-york/accordion.tsx`:

```tsx
<motion.div
  layout="size"
  initial={false}
  style={{ height: open ? contentHeight : 0 }}
  transition={getTransition(reduce, open)}
>
```

### 3g. `useReducedMotion` for accessibility

From `/home/himmel/personal/prsui/registry/new-york/accordion.tsx`:

```tsx
